{"word":"G3038 - λιθόστρωτος - lithóstrōtos - lith-os'-tro-tos - Pavement","slug":"G3038","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">λιθόστρωτος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>lithóstrōtos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>lith-os'-tro-tos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Pavement"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BB;&#x03B9;&#x03B8;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03C4;&#x03C1;&#x03C9;&#x03C4;&#x03BF;&#x03C2; - lithostro&#x0304;tos</b> - <i>lith-os'-tro-tos</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G3037\">G3037</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G4766\">G4766</a>; <i>stone strewed</i>, that is, a tessellated <i>mosaic</i> on which the Roman tribunal was placed: - Pavement."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3035\">G3035</a>, <a href=\"#/G3037\">G3037</a>"}]}